s://s.w.org/images/core/5.8/outside-03.jpg\" alt=\"The sun shining over a ridge leading down into the shore. In the distance, a car drives down a road.\" /></figure></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:33%\">\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-extra-small-font-size\" style=\"color:#000000\">Undoubtedly we have no questions to ask which are unanswerable. We must trust the perfection of the creation so far, as to believe that whatever curiosity the order of things has awakened in our minds, the order of things can satisfy. Every man&#8217;s condition is a solution in hieroglyphic to those inquiries he would put.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<style>.wp-container-623141bf8b09f {display: flex;gap: var( --wp--style--block-gap, 0.5em );flex-wrap: nowrap;align-items: center;}.wp-container-623141bf8b09f > * { margin: 0; }</style></div>\n<style>.wp-container-623141bf8b376 .alignleft { float: left; margin-right: 2em; margin-left: 0; }.wp-container-623141bf8b376 .alignright { float: right; margin-left: 2em; margin-right: 0; }.wp-container-623141bf8b376 > * { margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; }.wp-container-623141bf8b376 > * + * { margin-top: var( --wp--style--block-gap );  margin-bottom: 0; }</style>\";s:9:\"protected\";b:0;}s:4:\"meta\";O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:10:\"spay_email\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"wpop_keywords\";s:0:\"\";s:16:\"wpop_description\";s:77:\"Three columns with images and text, with vertical spacing for an offset look.\";s:19:\"wpop_viewport_width\";i:1200;s:16:\"wpop_block_types\";a:0:{}s:11:\"wpop_locale\";s:5:\"en_US\";s:20:\"wpop_unlisted_reason\";s:0:\"\";}s:14:\"category_slugs\";a:2:{i:0;s:7:\"columns\";i:1;s:8:\"featured\";}s:13:\"keyword_slugs\";a:1:{i:0;s:4:\"core\";}s:15:\"pattern_content\";s:3990:\"<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"full\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#f8f4e4\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-background\" style=\"background-color:#f8f4e4\"><!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\