(80, 1, '2022-03-14 07:19:30', '2022-03-14 07:19:30', '• Stunning displays: Choose an <strong>Android tablet</strong> with a brilliant display and you can watch your favorite content like never before with the wide viewing angle and the impressive HD visuals.\r\n• Powerful processor: Browse the web, check email and so much more, all at lightning-fast speeds. Tablets featuring Quad-Core processors save you valuable time with their impressive speed and power.\r\n• QuickRemote: Program and operate all of your electronic devices, right from your <strong>tablet</strong> with <strong>LG’s</strong> available QuickRemote feature.\r\n• Simplified multitasking: <strong>Android tablets</strong> with the available QSlide function allow you to switch between multiple apps at once for superior multi-tasking.\r\n• Dual Window™: Open two different apps on the expansive display, then drag and drop content between windows with this smart feature, available on many of our tablets.\r\n• Sleek designs: Smooth, rounded corners and slim profiles provide in-hand comfort and a stable grip.', 'LG G Pad™ 10.1', '<h1 id=\"product-info-V700\" class=\"model-title-desktop-pdp-new\">A tablet that makes life simple</h1>', 'trash', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lg-g-pad-10-1__trashed', '', '', '2022-03-15 00:25:43', '2022-03-15 00:25:43', '', 0, 'https://localhost/wp591/?post_type=product&#038;p=80', 0, 'product', '', 0),
