(87, 1, '2022-03-14 07:35:38', '2022-03-14 07:35:38', 'Zenfone 8 Flip defies ordinary to excel in everything it does. The innovative Flip Camera gives you professional-quality front or rear photos. There’s powerful performance from the Qualcomm® Snapdragon™ 888 5G Mobile Platform. It has a superb AMOLED display and delivers incredible endurance from its massive battery. Get ready to see, hear and interact with the world in an extraordinary way!\r\n\r\nPowerful and fast\r\nIt’s time to rev up your life with Zenfone 8 Flip, powered by the amazing Qualcomm® Snapdragon™ 888 5G Mobile Platform, with the fastest 5G speeds that let you download or share stuff in the blink of an eye. Zenfone 8 Flip also includes the latest WiFi 6E2 technology, powering your day with faster and more stable connections.\r\n\r\nEnjoy the freedom of Flip Camera! Triple Flip Camera\r\nWith Flip Camera’s unique triple-camera module, you get a 64 MP wide-angle main camera, an ultrawide-angle camera, and a telephoto camera. Its unrivaled quality and versatility lets you capture every memorable moment, perfectly.\r\nFlip Camera gives you the same high-resolution camera for front- and rear-facing shots, with all the same modes!\r\nZenfone 8 Flip has the highest-resolution camera of any current smartphone. And it takes ultrawide selfies that include everyone, with automatic face-distortion correction to keep your gang looking great!\r\nThe same camera system also takes amazing shots at night or in low-light situations. Night-time doesn’t have to be dark-time!', 'ASUS Zenfone 8 Flip ZS672KS', '8GB+256GB/SD 888/6.67\" AMOLED FHD 90Hz/64MP/5000mAh', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'asus-zenfone-8-flip-zs672ks', '', '', '2022-03-15 03:14:27', '2022-03-15 03:14:27', '', 0, 'https://localhost/wp591/?post_type=product&#038;p=87', 0, 'product', '', 0),
